reviewText: Sweet Temptation is a simple but very good movie with great performances by Rob Estes & Beverly D'Angelo. It provocative  , sexy ,  and keeps you  invested all the way to the end. If you are fan of lifetme movies, you will like this movie!
I bought this movie simply because it has my idol in it (actress turned singer/songwritter, Jenny Lewis).  I watched it and discovered that I actually loved the movie.  I never get tired ot it.

I love Rob Estes and think he is super hot which is why I like this movie.  If you aren't a fan of his, then skip it because you probably won't like it.  The plot is not that good and the writing is worse.
